    "description": {
      "value": "<h3 id=\"sorts-de-cercle\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><strong>Sorts de cercle D&eacute;sert</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Votre connexion mystique avec la terre vous donne la capacit&eacute; de lancer certains sorts. Aux niveaux 3, 5, 7 et 9, vous avez acc&egrave;s &agrave; des sorts de cercles li&eacute;s au type de terrain sur lequel vous &ecirc;tes devenu druide.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Une fois que vous avez appris un sort de cercle, il est toujours consid&eacute;r&eacute; comme pr&eacute;par&eacute; et il n'est pas comptabilis&eacute; dans le nombre de sorts que vous pouvez pr&eacute;parer chaque jour. Si vous apprenez un sort qui n'appara&icirc;t pas dans la liste de&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\" href=\"https://5e-drs.fr/grimoire/?classes=Druide\">sorts de druide</a>, consid&eacute;rez-le quand m&ecirc;me comme un sort de druide.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<table style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 365px; color: #2e1f49; font-family: Friz, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\n<thead style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">\n<th style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 106px;\">Niv. de druide</th>\n<th style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 256px;\">Sorts de cercle</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 104px;\">3</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 254px;\">@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.l8ovgCzZX50c8OYI]{Flou} @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.6CWJkMSqf6oyd6dm]{Silence}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 104px;\">5</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 254px;\">@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.nQsR7yLQIdhZ6GTJ]{Cr&eacute;ation de nourriture et d'eau} @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.adB2GwSHzktgDOYo]{Protection contre les &eacute;nergies}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 104px;\">7</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 254px;\">@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.EPBp6z2DP5yRO4J4]{Fl&eacute;trissement} @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.CQ0qnTBZGBIYsQp1]{Terrain hallucinatoire}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 104px;\">9</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; width: 254px;\">@UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.oE6gSp6l5nACXV0T]{Fl&eacute;au d'insectes} @UUID[Compendium.srd-heros-et-dragons.HnD-grimoire.ePo9ujJTwfxIc30x]{Mur de pierre}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
